[{"layout":"zeppelin","isRunnable":true,"template":"dsrgmn3y","templateConfig":"{\"visualization\":{\"filters\":[{\"_id\":1583324064459,\"type\":\"styling\",\"enabled\":true,\"conditions\":{\"operator\":\"and\",\"conditions\":[{\"property\":\"hiddenConnection\",\"operator\":\"*\",\"value\":\"\"}]},\"component\":\"edge\",\"target\":\"edge\",\"properties\":{\"colors\":[\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)\"],\"style\":[\"dashed\"],\"legendTitle\":[\"Hidden Connection\"]}},{\"_id\":1590499315755,\"type\":\"aggregation\",\"enabled\":true,\"conditions\":{\"operator\":\"and\",\"conditions\":[]},\"component\":\"vertex\",\"target\":\"vertex\",\"properties\":{},\"aggregation\":[{\"source\":\"\",\"type\":\"average\"}]}],\"version\":4}}","isEditable":true,"name":"08 - Demo Select AI Product Return Agent - Anon","description":null,"type":"medium","paragraphs":[{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"html","title":null,"message":["%md ","<center><h2 style='color:#0873d1'>Select AI - Create a Product Return Agent with Built-In Tools<h2><\/center>"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776963600600,"interpreter":"md.medium","endTime":1776963601070,"results":[{"message":"<center><h2 style='color:#0873d1'>Select AI - Create a Product Return Agent with Built-In Tools<h2><\/center>\n","type":"HTML"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":true,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":true,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"html","title":"Pre-Requisites - Configuring Select AI","message":["%md","","<b>Note:<\/b> Please refer to the `\"00 - Setup Select AI - Anon\"` Notebook for all pre-requisites on granting permissions to Packages, LLMs, Authentication and for Setting Up Credentials."],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964860613,"interpreter":"md.medium","endTime":1776964861075,"results":[{"message":"<p><b>Note:<\/b> Please refer to the <code>&quot;00 - Setup Select AI - Anon&quot;<\/code> Notebook for all pre-requisites on granting permissions to Packages, LLMs, Authentication and for Setting Up Credentials.<\/p>\n","type":"HTML"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":true,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":true,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"html","title":"Create a Product Return Agent with Built-In Tools","message":["%md","","This example shows how you can create a multi-turn conversational agent using Select AI Agent. In this example, you set up a customer-service agent that handles product returns and updates the return status in your database.<\/br><\/br>","","<b>Create an Agent<\/b>","","You create an agent called Customer_Return_Agent with a profile and role to manage return requests.<\/br><\/br>","","<b>Create Tools<\/b>","","You then create an agent tool named Update_Order_Status_Tool to update the status of the order in your database.<\/br><\/br>","","<b>Create Task<\/b>","","You create a task called Handle_Product_Return_Task to guide the flow: ask for the reason (no longer needed, arrived too late, box broken, or defective). Proceed with a defective return flow.<\/br><\/br>","","<b>Create Team<\/b>","","You create an agent team called Return_Agency_Team with Customer_Return_Agent as the agent and set it as an active team.<\/br><\/br>","","<b>Run the Select AI Agent Team<\/b>","","You now run the agent team by using select ai agent as a prefix to your prompts."],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1770141314941,"interpreter":"md.medium","endTime":1770141315375,"results":[{"message":"<p>This example shows how you can create a multi-turn conversational agent using Select AI Agent. In this example, you set up a customer-service agent that handles product returns and updates the return status in your database.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<p><b>Create an Agent<\/b><\/p>\n<p>You create an agent called Customer_Return_Agent with a profile and role to manage return requests.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<p><b>Create Tools<\/b><\/p>\n<p>You then create an agent tool named Update_Order_Status_Tool to update the status of the order in your database.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<p><b>Create Task<\/b><\/p>\n<p>You create a task called Handle_Product_Return_Task to guide the flow: ask for the reason (no longer needed, arrived too late, box broken, or defective). Proceed with a defective return flow.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<p><b>Create Team<\/b><\/p>\n<p>You create an agent team called Return_Agency_Team with Customer_Return_Agent as the agent and set it as an active team.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<p><b>Run the Select AI Agent Team<\/b><\/p>\n<p>You now run the agent team by using select ai agent as a prefix to your prompts.<\/p>\n","type":"HTML"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":true,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":true,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop Tables","message":["%script","","-- Drop Demo Tables If Exists","DROP TABLE IF EXISTS DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS;","DROP TABLE IF EXISTS DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS;"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776963754052,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776963754517,"results":[{"message":"\nTable DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS dropped.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\nTable DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS dropped.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create Tables & Insert Records","message":["%script","","-- Create Sample Customer Data","CREATE TABLE DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS (","    customer_id  NUMBER(10) PRIMARY KEY,","    name         VARCHAR2(100),","    email        VARCHAR2(100),","    phone        VARCHAR2(20),","    state        VARCHAR2(2),","    zip          VARCHAR2(10)",");","","INSERT INTO DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS (customer_id, name, email, phone, state, zip) VALUES","(1, 'Alice Thompson', 'alice.thompson@example.com', '555-1234', 'NY', '10001'),","(2, 'Bob Martinez', 'bob.martinez@example.com', '555-2345', 'CA', '94105'),","(3, 'Carol Chen', 'carol.chen@example.com', '555-3456', 'TX', '73301'),","(4, 'David Johnson', 'david.johnson@example.com', '555-4567', 'IL', '60601'),","(5, 'Eva Green', 'eva.green@example.com', '555-5678', 'FL', '33101');","","-- Create Sample Customer Order Status","CREATE TABLE DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS (","    customer_id     NUMBER(10),","    order_number    VARCHAR2(20),","    status          VARCHAR2(30),","    product_name    VARCHAR2(100)","",");","","INSERT INTO DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS (customer_id, order_number, status, product_name) VALUES","(2, '7734', 'delivered', 'smartphone charging cord'),","(1, '4381', 'pending_delivery', 'smartphone protective case'),","(2, '7820', 'delivered', 'smartphone charging cord'),","(3, '1293', 'pending_return', 'smartphone stand (metal)'),","(4, '9842', 'returned', 'smartphone backup storage'),","(5, '5019', 'delivered', 'smartphone protective case'),","(2, '6674', 'pending_delivery', 'smartphone charging cord'),","(1, '3087', 'returned', 'smartphone stand (metal)'),","(3, '7635', 'pending_return', 'smartphone backup storage'),","(4, '3928', 'delivered', 'smartphone protective case'),","(5, '8421', 'pending_delivery', 'smartphone charging cord'),","(1, '2204', 'returned', 'smartphone stand (metal)'),","(2, '7031', 'pending_delivery', 'smartphone backup storage'),","(3, '1649', 'delivered', 'smartphone protective case'),","(4, '9732', 'pending_return', 'smartphone charging cord'),","(5, '4550', 'delivered', 'smartphone stand (metal)'),","(1, '6468', 'pending_delivery', 'smartphone backup storage'),","(2, '3910', 'returned', 'smartphone protective case'),","(3, '2187', 'delivered', 'smartphone charging cord'),","(4, '8023', 'pending_return', 'smartphone stand (metal)'),","(5, '5176', 'delivered', 'smartphone backup storage');","","-- COMMIT","COMMIT;"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776963821398,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776963822691,"results":[{"message":"\nTable DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS created.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\n5 rows inserted.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\nTable DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS created.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\n21 rows inserted.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":null,"title":"Define OCI API Credential","message":["%script","","-- Drop Credential","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD.DROP_CREDENTIAL('<enter-oci-api-credential-name>');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Credential does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":null,"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":null,"row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":null},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":null,"title":null,"message":["%script","","-- Create Credentials for OCI API Key","BEGIN                                                                          ","\tDBMS_CLOUD.CREATE_CREDENTIAL","        (  ","\t\t    \tcredential_name => '<enter-oci-api-credential-name>',","\t\t\t \tuser_ocid \t\t=> '<enter-user-ocid>',","\t\t        tenancy_ocid    => '<enter-tenancy-ocid>',","\t\t        private_key     => '<enter-private-key-value>',","\t\t        fingerprint     => '<enter-private-key-fingerprint>'       ","        );                                                                           ","END;                                                                           ","/"],"enabled":true,"result":null,"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":null,"row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":null},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Define AI Profile","message":["%script","","-- Drop AI Profile","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI.DROP_PROFILE('<enter-ai-profile-name>');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Profile does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776963854672,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776963856666,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":null,"message":["%script","","-- Create AI Profile","BEGIN                                                                          ","\tDBMS_CLOUD_AI.CREATE_PROFILE","        (                                                ","\t\t        profile_name => '<enter-ai-profile-name>'","\t\t    ,   attributes   => '{","                                        \"provider\"          : \"oci\"","\t\t                            ,   \"object_list\"       : ","                                                                [","                                                                        {\"owner\": \"<enter-schema-name>\", \"name\": \"DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS\"}","                                                                    ,   {\"owner\": \"<enter-schema-name>\", \"name\": \"DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS\"}","                                                                ]","                                    ,   \"credential_name\"   : \"<enter-oci-api-credential-name>\"","                                    ,   \"model\"             : \"<enter-model-name-id>\"","                                    ,   \"oci_compartment_id\": \"<enter-compartment-ocid>\"","                                    ,   \"region\"            : \"<enter-region-identifier>\"","                                    ,   \"comments\"          : \"true\"","                                    ,   \"conversation\"      : \"true\"","                                }'","        );","END;                                                                           ","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776963874620,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776963876192,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Define PL/SQL Function to Update Order Status","message":["%script","","-- Drop PL/SQL Function that will be used to update order status","DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS UPDATE_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS;"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964049468,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964049928,"results":[{"message":"\nFunction UPDATE_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS dropped.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":null,"message":["%script","-- A Function returns something, Procedure doesn't","","--Create a update customer order status function","CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION UPDATE_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS (","    p_customer_name IN VARCHAR2,","    p_order_number  IN VARCHAR2,","    p_status        IN VARCHAR2",") RETURN VARCHAR2 IS","","    -- Global variables","    v_customer_id  DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS.customer_id%TYPE;","    v_row_count    NUMBER;","","BEGIN","    -- Find customer_id from customer_name","    SELECT customer_id","    INTO v_customer_id","    FROM DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMERS","    WHERE name = p_customer_name;","    ","    UPDATE DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS","    SET status = p_status","    WHERE customer_id = v_customer_id","      AND order_number = p_order_number;","","    v_row_count := SQL%ROWCOUNT;","","    IF v_row_count = 0 THEN","        RETURN 'No matching record found to update.';","    ELSE","        RETURN 'Update successful.';","    END IF;","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        RETURN 'Error: ' || SQLERRM;","END;"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964146863,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964147421,"results":[{"message":"\nFunction UPDATE_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS compiled\n\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"table","title":"View Record","message":["%sql","","-- Preview an example record"," SELECT * FROM DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 3 AND ORDER_NUMBER = '2187';"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964179398,"interpreter":"sql.medium","endTime":1776964179790,"results":[{"message":"CUSTOMER_ID\tORDER_NUMBER\tSTATUS\tPRODUCT_NAME\n3\t2187\tdelivered\tsmartphone charging cord\n","type":"TABLE"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Test PL/SQL Function","message":["%script","","-- Test PL/SQL Function Defined Above","DECLARE","    v_result VARCHAR2;","BEGIN","    v_result := UPDATE_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS('Carol Chen', '2187', 'no longer needed');","","    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE(v_result);","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964207304,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964207760,"results":[{"message":"Update successful.\n\n\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"table","title":"View Record","message":["%sql","","-- Preview updated record"," SELECT * FROM DEMO_AGENTS_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 3 AND ORDER_NUMBER = '2187';"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964217810,"interpreter":"sql.medium","endTime":1776964218238,"results":[{"message":"CUSTOMER_ID\tORDER_NUMBER\tSTATUS\tPRODUCT_NAME\n3\t2187\tno longer needed\tsmartphone charging cord\n","type":"TABLE"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Define Update Order Status Tool","message":["%script","","-- Drop Agent Tool","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_TOOL('UPDATE_ORDER_STATUS_TOOL');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Tool does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964245132,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964245688,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":null,"message":["%script","","--Create Agent Tool","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_TOOL(","        tool_name => 'UPDATE_ORDER_STATUS_TOOL',","        attributes => '{\"instruction\": \"This tool updates the database to reflect return status change. Always confirm user name and order number with user before updating status\",","                        \"function\" : \"UPDATE_CUSTOMER_ORDER_STATUS\"}',","        description => 'Tool for updating customer order status in database table.'","    );","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964347959,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964348493,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Define Handle Product Return Task","message":["%script","","-- Drop Agent Task","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_TASK('HANDLE_PRODUCT_RETURN_TASK');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Task does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964405073,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964405580,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":null,"message":["%script","","-- Create Agent Task","BEGIN","  DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_TASK(","    task_name => 'HANDLE_PRODUCT_RETURN_TASK',","    attributes => '{\"instruction\": \"Process a product return request from a customer: {query}' || ","                    '1. Ask customer the order reason for return (no longer needed, arrived too late, box broken, or defective)' || ","                    '2. If no longer needed:' ||","                    '   a. Inform customer to ship the product at their expense back to us.' ||","                    '   b. Update the order status to return_shipment_pending using UPDATE_ORDER_STATUS_TOOL.' ||","                     '3. If it arrived too late:' ||","                    '   a. Ask customer if they want a refund.' ||","                    '   b. If the customer wants a refund, then confirm refund processed and update the order status to refund_completed' || ","                    '4. If the product was defective or the box broken:' ||","                    '   a. Ask customer if they want a replacement or a refund' ||","                    '   b. If a replacement, inform customer replacement is on its way and they will receive a return shipping label for the defective product, then update the order status to replaced' ||","                    '   c. If a refund, inform customer to print out the return shipping label for the defective product, return the product, and update the order status to refund' ||","                    '5. After the completion of a return or refund, ask if you can help with anything else.' ||","                    '   End the task if user does not need help on anything else\",","                    \"tools\": [\"UPDATE_ORDER_STATUS_TOOL\"]}'","  );","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964484610,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964485226,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Define Customer Return Agent","message":["%script","","-- Drop Agent","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_AGENT('CUSTOMER_RETURN_AGENT');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Agent does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964521909,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964522428,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":null,"message":["%script","","-- Create Agent","BEGIN","  DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_AGENT(","    agent_name => 'CUSTOMER_RETURN_AGENT',","    attributes => '{\"profile_name\": \"<enter-ai-profile-name>\",","                    \"role\": \"You are an experienced customer return agent who deals with customers return requests.\"}');","END;","/"," "],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964532569,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964533134,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Define Return Agency Team","message":["%script","","-- Drop Agent Team","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_TEAM('RETURN_AGENCY_TEAM');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Agent Team does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776964556446,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776964557637,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":null,"message":["%script","","-- Create Agent Team","BEGIN                                                                ","  DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREA